A section of Muslim clerics have endorsed Mombasa Gema chairman Crispus Waithaka (pictured) for Nyali MP.This comes two days after Waithaka invited Jubilee s Mombasa governor hopeful Suleiman Shahbal to the PCEA Makupa Church on Sunday. We have been impressed by his statement on the unity of both Christians and Muslims, Sheikh Mahamoud Awadh said.